{"tid":1441971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(轉載）（救恩堂）搞聯署對任何包裝的暴力說不","createTime":"2019-08-10T19:20:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T10:41:14.000Z","uid":186955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4b66f8efdb0e8d92fdb705359d1cf87489dcca4a","tid":1441971,"uid":186955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T19:20:36.000Z","msg":"大部份發起人都是救恩堂的牧者，是非不分。感恩我已轉堂，不再是受這些牧者&quot;牧養&rdquo;。請這些牧者搞清楚，要譴責的是這政府，他們才是一切暴力來源。是天真還是無知?要譴責的是暴力的來源，沒有真正處理問題的源頭，叫受傷者的自衛說不?香港真的可以回復安寧?是無知也是自欺，自從政府默許黑警合作又不作獨立調查那刻，香港已不能回復原狀，除非政府真的回應訴求。現時抗爭者只是用自己的身體維護香港包括批評他們的人。如果今次失守了，更大的壓迫及、貪腐及不公將會無日無知。這班聯署及發起人將背負同樣的責任。<br />\n再者看看聯署的有，陳世強（推薦何君堯的人），吳宗民及梁燕城，你便知這聯署背後的毒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/308959215866194/posts/2365080946920667/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F308959215866194%2Fposts%2F2365080946920667%2F&d=y7g0wjbeyFmnVC7InFCgMsF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=94de2040\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/308959215866194/posts/2365080946920667/</a>"},{"pid":"a24fcb2beaa61f3192ca7f966dfb2883bce531ff","tid":1441971,"uid":186955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T19:23:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KhHnUvO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKhHnUvO.png&h=6aa622cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-jwpdxxmvUo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-jwpdxxmvUo&d=y7g0wjbeyFmnVC7InFCgMsF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=2f6c4b40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-jwpdxxmvUo</a>"},{"pid":"a6d81318cdae897eae9d9591d802d55ff4103703","tid":1441971,"uid":10289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T19:24:28.000Z","msg":"得連登仔知唔夠架<br />\n<br />\n［文宣唔夠快］［地區工作］可唔可以俾啲時間文宣組？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1441906\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1441906</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"74166cf1dca8